  "patient_text_brief": "Child: Rohan Kumar, 2-year-old boy.\n\nMain problem:\n- He has been vomiting for the last 3 days.\n- It started suddenly and is getting a bit better.\n- The amount each time is moderate.\n\nOther problems (only if asked):\n- Loose watery stools for 2 days, about 5 to 10 times a day.\n- No blood in stools.\n- He has fever.\n- He complains of stomach pain.\n- He looks weak and is not eating well.\n- He has lost some weight.\n- He feels dizzy sometimes.\n\nPast history:\n- No similar illness before.\n- No known allergies.\n- No regular medicines.\n- No medicines given at home this time.\n- Vaccinations are not fully up to date.\n\nLifestyle:\n- Eats a mixed diet.\n- Hygiene at home is not very good.",
